936
00:33:46,290 --> 00:33:47,792
The rest is mine.

937
00:33:48,459 --> 00:33:50,695
NAM-NO'S PORTION

938
00:33:50,762 --> 00:33:52,430
Hurry up. 27 seconds.

939
00:33:52,497 --> 00:33:54,165
-Twenty-seven seconds.
-Twenty seconds.

940
00:33:55,366 --> 00:33:56,367
