952
00:34:17,121 --> 00:34:19,390
-Eight. Seven.
-Ring the bell!

953
00:34:19,457 --> 00:34:21,926
-Eight. Seven.
-Ring the bell!

954
00:34:21,993 --> 00:34:24,328
-Six. Five. Four.
-Ring it first!

955
00:34:24,395 --> 00:34:25,363
-Three.
-Three.

956
00:34:25,663 --> 00:34:28,599
